Files Included :

.c Files :

	1. diningPhilosopher.c
	2. monitor.c

.h Files :

	1. monitor.h

Other files:
	
	1. Makefile
	2. readme file

Compiling:
	
	The Makefile contains the commands for compiling the source files.
	To compile enter the following command.

	$ make
	
	This will create diningPhilosopher.o, monitor.o, and an executable file philosopher_yj

Clean: 

	To clean enter the following command.

	$ make clean

	This will remove the obj files and the executable file philosopher_yj

Execute:

	To execute enter the following
	
	$ ./philosopher_yj


Cases Handled :

	-solution for Dining Philosophers problem is implemented using monitor.
	-Monitor implemented using semaphores.
	-starvation problem also handled using turn variable corresponding to each chopstick.
